gov.llnl.ontology.wordnet
Interface Lemma

All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseLemma
public interface Lemma

This interface represents a single term that maps to a Synset in the WordNet dictionary.

Each Lemma has several attributes:
  • A key that uniquely identifies this Lemma against other Lemmas for the same Synset.
  • The Synset for this Lemma
  • The name of this Lemma
  • The lexigicgrapher file name that is attributed to this Lemma
  • The lexigicgrapher file name index that is attributed to this Lemma
  • The lexigicgrapher index that is attributed to this Lemma

Author:
Keith Stevens
